basic.Peptide Name: AI18 (AI Predicted AMPs, Arg-rich, UCLL1c, XXA)
basic.Target Organism: Active against E. faecalis ATCC 29212 (MIC 32 ug/ml), S. aureus ATCC 29213 (MIC 32 ug/ml), K. pneumoniae ATCC 700603 and 3 resistant strains (MIC 8-32 ug/ml), A. baumannii  ATCC 19606 or MDR 316039 (8 ug/ml), P. aeruginosa ATCC 27853 or MDR 304238 (MIC 8-16 ug/ml), E. coli ATCC 25922 or MDR 103231 (MIC 4-8 ug/ml).
